this and nor do we believe that it is possible to achieve this through the creation of artificial \'91fire walls\'92.}}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f4\fs24\lang1033\i0\b0{\super \chftn{\*\footnote \chftn\pard\plain \ltrpar\s14{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\ql\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\loch{\*\cs23\cf0{\*\updnprop5801}\up8\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\loch}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch  }{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f4\fs20\lang1033\i0\b0{\cf1 The US Federal Trade Commission recently considered a vertical transaction between the Ingram Book Group and Barnes & Noble, respectively the largest wholesaler and retailer of books in the United States.  The transaction appears to have been withdrawn at
