ioral rules \'94- }{\cf1\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\i\loch\i The Evolving Approach to Merger Remedies by Richard G. Parker & David A. Balto, published in Antitrust Report (May 2000).}{\cf1 .}}}}
