{\*\cs23\cf0{\*\updnprop5801}\up10\rtlch\af6\afs24\lang255\ltrch\dbch\af6\langfe255\hich\f1\fs24\lang7177\loch\f1\fs24\lang7177 }  Note that there is no certainty that PD\'92s competitors will respond to this strategy by taking market share from PD.  Certain of PD\'92s competitors have already intimated th
